{"tid":233211,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"班藍屍拍嗰套 《血傘》 幾時上映?","createTime":"2017-05-07T11:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T11:31:51.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"225b91f0e9b5c33ca5b55836facc9bbcc1bb4f4f","tid":233211,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161029/large/1477730438_3d2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161029%2Flarge%2F1477730438_3d2d.jpg&h=a389ce0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話拍既，呃鳩我<br />\n<br />\n<strong>【「唔係想撼《十年》」】《血傘》只求上映五日 目標擸金像獎<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n黃夏蕙同契女艾美琦（Amy）今日喺銅鑼灣出席「傷健共融日2016」，提到聲稱以60萬開拍嘅大電影《血傘》（故事講述「港獨」10年後嘅境況），佢哋都話肯定會參演，夏蕙BB將飾演「吳方安心」，Amy就演政黨憤青，Amy自爆接拍後收到好多騷擾電話，仲被粗口辱罵，她稱電影題材敏感，又謂擔心拍完該片後會喺香港消失。<br />\n<br />\n黃夏蕙就話：「我一日畀人鬧，做嘢唔好醜化人，公道自在人心。只要唔好妖言惑眾，唔好過份，搞挑剔就得。」<br />\n<br />\n而導演之一嘅小肥豬Simon聲稱將攞60萬投資開戲，仲會做監製同導演（另一導演「正義聯盟」副主席係蔡克健），Simon話今次碌好多人情卡，所以60萬都可以拍到大電影，仲爆夏蕙BB三千蚊一組戲，每日拍六個鐘，而招募緊嘅演員價就$1,500至$1,800一組。<br />\n<br />\nSimon話：「今次係想創造香港機會，希望本土新人參與，部戲敏感，唔想演員政治化。兩邊都講，以和為貴。」佢仲話希望憑呢部戲攞金像獎㗎，仲話目前係希望電影喺戲院上到5日，但就講明唔係想撼《十年》喎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20161029/55844370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20161029%2F55844370&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ead52310\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20161029%2F55844370&h=32a23c2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20161029/55844370</a>"},{"pid":"e2c3a84445262e1d88468c8e787f73859dfa0d96","tid":233211,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"搵老細泵完水仲唔走數咩"},{"pid":"fa3cc60053ca7d37000c5f276eff3d6cfacb7566","tid":233211,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:31:51.000Z","msg":"正式褫奪黃夏蕙條老妖嘅bb頭銜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}